# Scoring parameters file, for use with TD learning 
#
# Scores are given in 1/1000 of a pawn.  The second number
# is either a 1 or 0.  1 = learn this parameter. 0 = don't learn.
# For the program to work properly, PAWN_VALUE must stay 1000
# Updates are roughly 10 points each, so learning piece values
# from zero will take a very long time
#
# If this file is deleted, a new one will be created with the defaults
#
# See search.par for a global variable to turn learning on/off

VERSION 6.1
PAWN_VALUE 1000 0
KING_VALUE 100000 1
KNIGHT_VALUE 4580 1
BISHOP_VALUE 4890 1
ROOK_VALUE 7110 1
QUEEN_VALUE 14980 1
